== BMC ITSM7 Alternate Approver Lookup
Returns the Login IDs for all current AP:Alternate records 
for the specified Login ID

For more information, see the Detailed Description section below.

=== Parameters
[Approver ID]
	Remedy Login ID of the individual to find alternates for

=== Sample Configuration
Approver ID::       Allen

=== Results
[Alternate Exists]
  Returns a Yes if current alternates are found and a No if no
  current alternates are found
[Login IDs]
  The login ids of the alternates found

=== Detailed Description
This handler returns the login ids for all alternates found.  
This is returned in XML format (like below) for use in loops.

<Login_Ids>
	<LoginId>Mary</LoginId>
	<LoginId>John</LoginId>
	<LoginId>Frank</LoginId>
</Login_Ids>
